metadata.title: Beringian Seabird Colony Catalog

creators.name: Division of Migratory Bird Management, US Fish

metadata.description: To estimate the size and composition of breeding populations of all seabird species. Data include locations and sizes of breeding colonies (approximately 1,600 in Alaska and 500 in Russia).
